text: The.Civic Solidarity Party () is a nationalist and conservative political party in Azerbaijan. It was founded in 1992."Head" The party's leader is Sabir Rustamkhanli, who is actually a poet. The party's ideology is based on the universal political values of freedom, equality and solidarity."Manifesto" At the 2020 parliamentary elections, it won 3 out of 125 seats. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:Political parties in Azerbaijan Category:Nationalist organizations in Azerbaijan Category:Conservative parties
